extendedInfo.description: This app will halp you find some fun productive stuff you can do with your time!You'll find the things you always wanted to learn but didn't know where to look for, The hobbies that fit you exactly, but you didn't know existed,The little upgrade that can make your day. All you have to do is choose... You can learn:- Origami! The art of paper folding- Doing magic!- How to play the guitar- Balloon folding! How to make shapes out of balloons- How to build a website!- Learn how to start your own blog and even to make money out of it.- Learn how to use PhotoShop- How to sketch a portrait- And more...Ever wanted to play the guitar? tried to use photoshop but it seems too complicated? have you ever tried real origami (there are some complex amazing origami art you can learn, you can make learn magic or many other great stuff to do with your time.keywords you can find in our app: photoshop origami time money blog guitar stuff magic hobby balloon portrait shape website paper folding
